package.name: Nektria_ReCS
package.summary: Let your customers choose the day and time they will receive their order.
package.description:
With a subscription to our service, you will be able to offer to your customers the option to choose the day and time they want to receive their order. Nektria will manage completely the delivery of your products so you can focus on what you do the best: selling.
RECShipping will integrate seemlessly with your existing shipping options offering an additional, more convenient alternative in the big cities that are covered by our service. Then, you can choose to use or not our standard delivery service to reach every area of the Spanish mainland territory.
Choose the theme that best fits your shop !
more information on our website: http://www.recshipping.com/
Note: Our extension is compatible with the LightCheckout module!
package.notes: Improvements in the widget and compatibility across Magento versions.
